OL,3,CSarwar pledges to slash NHS waiting
OL,4,Ctimes and end 8am GP appointment
OL,5,C'scramble'
OL,7,FAnas Sarwar has pledged to slash
OL,8,Fwaiting times and end the 8am
OL,9,F"scramble" for a GP appointment as
OL,10,Fpart of his party's plans to "fix the
OL,11,Fmess" in the health service.
OL,13,FAs the Holyrood election campaign
OL,14,Fenters its first weekend, the Scottish
OL,15,FLabour leader said "people feel
OL,16,FScotland is stuck" after two decades
OL,17,Fof the SNP ` and that this is "no
OL,18,Fclearer than in our NHS".
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@JO]rD@^OUsD@EO]wD@TOUxD@RO]yD@
OL,26,A_OUzD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774663388
OL,3,CSarwar pledges to slash NHS waiting
OL,4,Ctimes and end 8am GP appointment
OL,5,C'scramble'
OL,7,FHe said if his party is elected it
OL,8,Fwould "get the basics right" with a
OL,9,Fplan that includes slashing waiting
OL,10,Ftimes, bringing back the family doctor
OL,11,Fand using new technology to speed up
OL,12,Fdiagnosis and treatment.
OL,14,FIt would also see the creation of
OL,15,Fskilled jobs with 9,000 new
OL,16,Fapprenticeships, and the building of
OL,17,Fnew homes and the cutting of
OL,18,FGovernment waste to make life more
OL,19,Faffordable, Mr Sarwar said.
OL,26,@pD@GOUpD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774663388
OL,3,CSarwar pledges to slash NHS waiting
OL,4,Ctimes and end 8am GP appointment
OL,5,C'scramble'
OL,7,FHe added: "After 20 years of the SNP,
OL,8,Ftoo many people feel Scotland is
OL,9,Fstuck, and nowhere is that clearer
OL,10,Fthan in our NHS.
OL,12,F"Waiting lists are soaring, patients
OL,13,Fare being let down and the SNP has run
OL,14,Fout of road.
OL,16,F"I'm standing to fix the mess, get the
OL,17,Fbasics right and build a better future
OL,18,Ffor Scotland.
OL,26,@oD@KOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774663388
OL,3,CSarwar pledges to slash NHS waiting
OL,4,Ctimes and end 8am GP appointment
OL,5,C'scramble'
OL,7,F"That starts with an NHS that is there
OL,8,Fwhen you need it, cutting waiting
OL,9,Flists, ending the scramble for a GP
OL,10,Fappointment and bringing back the
OL,11,Ffamily doctor.
OL,13,F"But it also means creating more
OL,14,Fopportunity, making life more
OL,15,Faffordable and making sure government
OL,16,Fis focused on the priorities of
OL,17,Fworking people.
OL,19,F"On May 7, vote Scottish Labour on
OL,20,Fboth votes for the change Scotland
OL,21,Fneeds."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU{D@AOU}D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
