OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774663388
OL,3,CSarwar pledges to slash NHS waiting
OL,4,Ctimes and end 8am GP appointment
OL,5,C'scramble'
OL,7,FLabour pointed out that despite SNP
OL,8,Fpromises of an NHS recovery plan in
OL,9,F2021, waiting lists have risen by more
OL,10,Fthan 237,000, and there are now
OL,11,F780,000 ongoing "waits" in NHS
OL,12,FScotland.
OL,14,FThe number of waits of more than two
OL,15,Fyears has also risen five-fold since
OL,16,Fthe last election, from 1,200 in 2021
OL,17,Fto 6,400 today.
OL,26,@sD@QOUsD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
