OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774663388
OL,3,CSarwar pledges to slash NHS waiting
OL,4,Ctimes and end 8am GP appointment
OL,5,C'scramble'
OL,7,FMr Sarwar will tell voters on Saturday
OL,8,Fthat as a former NHS dentist the
OL,9,F"crisis" facing the health service is
OL,10,F"personal" to him, and that Scotland
OL,11,Fcannot afford another five years of
OL,12,Fthe same.
OL,14,FHealth Secretary Neil Gray insisted
OL,15,Fthat under under John Swinney's
OL,16,Fleadership the NHS has "turned a
OL,17,Fcorner".
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@HO]rD@AOUrD@JO]xD@XOUyD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
