OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774663388
OL,3,CSarwar pledges to slash NHS waiting
OL,4,Ctimes and end 8am GP appointment
OL,5,C'scramble'
OL,7,F"Waiting times are down, GP numbers
OL,8,Fare up, thousands more operations are
OL,9,Fbeing performed and walk-in GP centres
OL,10,Fare opening in communities across the
OL,11,Fcountry," he said.
OL,13,F"Meanwhile all Labour can do is attack
OL,14,Four NHS, with some even going as far
OL,15,Fas to say they would ditch the GP walk-
OL,16,Fin clinics.
OL,18,F"On May 7, people in Scotland can
OL,19,Fchoose John Swinney's strong
OL,20,Fleadership, which is delivering for
OL,21,Four NHS."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@IO]uD@AOUzD@AOU}D@IO]
